## 4. HOW TO ADD PROJECT SCREENSHOTS
1. Take a screenshot of the live project.
2. Host it on Cloudinary / Imgbb / GitHub repo (public) / your own server.
3. In the HTML, find `data-img="PLACEHOLDER"` for that project card.
4. Replace `PLACEHOLDER` with your image URL.

Or tell an AI: *"Replace the image for ZRM with this URL: https://..."*

