## 9. DESIGN / THEME CUSTOMIZATION
The portfolio uses CSS variables at the top of the `<style>` block:

```css
--bg:        #0a0a0f   /* main dark background */
--surface:   #13131a   /* card/panel background */
--border:    #1e1e2e   /* border color */
--text:      #e8e8f0   /* primary text */
--muted:     #6b6b8a   /* secondary/muted text */
--accent:    #00d4ff   /* primary cyan accent */
--accent2:   #7c3aed   /* secondary violet accent */
```

To change the accent color, update `--accent` and `--accent2`.
To switch to a light theme, change `--bg` to `#f9f9fb` and `--text` to `#111`.

